videos.headline: Syracuse QB Dungey's heave sets up rush TD
videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey rolls right and throws a pass downfield to Jamal Custis for a 44-yard gain, setting up Abdul Adams' 4-yard punch-in.

videos.headline: Dungey's errant pass is picked in Syracuse territory
videos.description: Eric Dungey commits Syracuse's first turnover of the game on an errant pass that is picked off by WVU's Kenny Robinson Jr. just inside the Orange's 20-yard line.

videos.headline: WVU's McKoy cashes in on wildcat TD
videos.description: West Virginia breaks out a wildcat formation on 3rd-and-goal and call Kennedy McKoy's number, who dives into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: WVU's Robinson ejected for late hit on Harris' head
videos.description: Syracuse's Taj Harris catches a pass, gets out of bounds and is cracked late in the head by Kenny Robinson Jr., who is ejected for targeting.

videos.headline: Syracuse DT leads charge on Adams' 2nd TD
videos.description: Syracuse implements DT Chris Elmore on offense to lead Abdul Adams' 1-yard touchdown run, his second of the game.

videos.headline: Dungey's back-shoulder ball on the money for TD
videos.description: Syracuse regains the lead over WVU on Eric Dungey's 13-yard touchdown strike to Trishton Jackson.

videos.headline: WVU QB Allison picked off on dropped pass
videos.description: WVU QB Jack Allison steps up in the pocket and fires a pass through his receiver's hands and is picked off by Allen Stritzinger.

videos.headline: Babers on 10-win season: Twice as good as a 9-win season
videos.description: Syracuse head coach Dino Babers is proud of his team, led by senior Eric Dungey, for the program's first 10-win season since 2001.

videos.headline: Syracuse's late surge seals Camping World Bowl win over WVU
videos.description: Syracuse's big plays and balanced attack gives the Orange a 34-18 victory vs. West Virginia in the Camping World Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Syracuse’s late surge seals Camping World Bowl win over WVU) 2018/12/28 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Dungey gets emotional after final game with Syracuse
videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey begins to cry when he discusses everything he's been through and the belief coach Dino Babers has in him.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Dungey gets emotional after final game with Syracuse) 2018/12/28
